summary: Finally finished her! I actually struggled a lot with this one. ;;_;; Not only did the ink somehow layer really weird but the...
caption:
Finally finished her! I actually struggled a lot with this one. ;;_;; Not only did the ink somehow layer really weird but the paper also warped in a strange way. Idk, maybe I damaged the paper? 🤔 Nevertheless, I still decided to post her cuz things simply go wrong somethimes. And even If I see a lot of mistakes and things that bother me - the piece as a whole STILL turned out alright! 🤗

Btw, feel free to check out my Instagram | My Twitter | Or My other art! ❤✨
Do NOT remove me as source or repost the picture.

summary: Weekly Update
body:
Weekly Update

Hello all!

It is really toasty where I live, which is normal for summer but it doesn’t mean I have to take it lying down!

Staying cool and hydrated though, so no worries!

In other news, my Patreon is about to hit its first goal! When the goal is reached, I will be offering a monthly stickers by mail reward for $10 where I will ship at least 2 stickers a month to those in that reward tier!

My Patreon offers lots of cool perks if you didn’t know!

From $1 per month you have access to all current wips and artworks for the month in a monthly dropbox! (On Tumblr the art being posted is approx 1-3 months old! Even then some works won’t be posted on Tumblr at all!)

Soon I will be posting Patreon-only progress videos for Patrons $3 and up!

There are also commission discounts on sketches and flat color chibis!

Also, all Patrons are invited to my Discord where I mostly talk about food and when I will next get to eat food. Important stuff!!

You can check me out there @ patreon.com/Dewdlepies

In other news, I have been very very busy doing the arts! I will start streaming again soon!
